{"tid":2377333,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[RTHK港台電視3]我煮場Cooking Family","createTime":"2021-01-23T13:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T14:39:57.000Z","uid":30,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0015a1a72b7353e4e6bc76553852d77158c998","tid":2377333,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"過去一年，大家都過着「隔離」或「半隔離」的生活，沒法跟同事、同學和友人一起吃喝玩樂。留家抗疫，使美食再次成為一家人重要的連結。＜我煮場 Cooking Family&gt;希望讓觀眾感受家常小菜的溫度，每集邀請兩個家庭參加，限時合作煮出兩道家常小菜。"},{"pid":"e623bb6419ae271441e7980fc45cdcfb4318659b","tid":2377333,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:54:01.000Z","msg":"【大細嚿 VS Roger Roger】（上集）<br />\n<br />\n參賽嘉賓：<br />\n【大細嚿】朱栢康與朱栢謙<br />\n【Roger Roger】韋羅莎(Rosa)與張銘耀(German)<br />\n<br />\n指定食材：洋蔥<br />\n<br />\n今集的煮場由朱栢康與朱栢謙，決戰好朋友韋羅莎(Rosa)與張銘耀(German)。擅長煮通粉的朱謙，夥拍只懂「白烚」的弟弟朱康，兩兄弟會煮出怎樣的家常小菜？從不下廚的Rosa，破天荒與大廚級老公German合作，變身成為一位小助手，是神助攻還是豬隊友？烹飪跟演戲一樣，每次把不同的素材放在一起，每個作品便會呈現不同的味道。兩組戲劇界家庭，今次又會上演一齣怎樣的好戲？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_1_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fcookingfamily%2F%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_9163_724684_1_l.jpg&h=e20c2648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_2_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fcookingfamily%2F%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_9163_724684_2_l.jpg&h=093b9d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_3_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fcookingfamily%2F%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_9163_724684_3_l.jpg&h=e6f9f675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_4_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fcookingfamily%2F%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_9163_724684_4_l.jpg&h=0425ed0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_5_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fcookingfamily%2F%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_9163_724684_5_l.jpg&h=ebe78632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_6_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fcookingfamily%2F%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_9163_724684_6_l.jpg&h=00d03d31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_7_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fcookingfamily%2F%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_9163_724684_7_l.jpg&h=ef12560f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_8_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fcookingfamily%2F%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_9163_724684_8_l.jpg&h=1e190d82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_9_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fcookingfamily%2F%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_9163_724684_9_l.jpg&h=f1db66bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/cookingfamily//originals/mfile_9163_724684_10_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=